<td class="mbox-text" style="">It has been suggested that <i><a href="/wiki/Carbon_offset" title="Carbon offset">Carbon offset</a></i> be <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Merging_and_moving_pages" title="Wikipedia:Merging and moving pages" class="mw-redirect">merged</a> into this article or section. (<a href="/wiki/Talk:Carbon_credit" title="Talk:Carbon credit">Discuss</a>)</td>
