<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Carbon_credit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.grist.org/advice/ask/2008/06/30/?source=ask" class="external text" title="http://www.grist.org/advice/ask/2008/06/30/?source=ask" rel="nofollow">Differences between carbon credit and carbon offsets</a>.</li>
